{"tid":2394853,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"福山雅治再演《伽利略》救亡","createTime":"2021-02-04T13:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T13:42:42.000Z","uid":47132,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"90960a13e3b4ba58b40e369dd2b8047944f5d135","tid":2394853,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.3dmgame.com/uploads/allimg/140901/223-140Z1221431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.3dmgame.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F140901%2F223-140Z1221431.jpg&h=b22facc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後日滿52歲日本男神福山雅治被爆再接拍《神探伽利略》系列，全新電影版暫定明年秋天上映，好拍檔柴咲幸亦會回歸，屆時更會推出同系列的全新單元劇，一於雙線出擊。據雜誌《週刊女性》報道，福山雅治主演的《神探伽利略》第三套電影版將於6月開鏡，望挽救近年低迷的演藝事業。<br />\n<br />\n福山自2015年與女星吹石一惠閃婚後，其人氣急速下滑，所以決定再接拍《伽利略》系列收復失地。《伽利略》2007年首套劇集大受歡迎，十集平均收視有21.9%，並在2013年添食，改由吉高由里子做女主角，平均收視亦達19.9%，而兩度搬上大銀幕分別大收49億日圓（約3.62億港元）及33億日圓（約2.44億港元）票房。"},{"pid":"f942c6e9318e7e077db615914dc0d90b28fd2190","tid":2394853,"uid":236891,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拍埋Legal High"},{"pid":"feee28cc47d154810bf5ce69f08583a880189f85","tid":2394853,"uid":111955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:22:16.000Z","msg":"應該係拍早2-3年既小說《沉默的遊行》"},{"pid":"29acc863cb8993b019baf98859eecaef920074ca","tid":2394853,"uid":269707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:24:10.000Z","msg":"終於，中五果年第二季之後除咗真夏方程式就冇，終於等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec356aa8e4e05d44a8040e5b6e8caeb302f9252b","tid":2394853,"uid":65384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"期待內海同湯川老師組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20277e2fba206732de3f92fff2bfd38240fc9ed","tid":2394853,"uid":2545,"like":